flowchart TD

    Start([Staff starts a new booking]) --> Login{Staff logged in?}
    Login -- No --> DoLogin[Staff logs in<br/>username + password]
    DoLogin --> Login
    Login -- Yes --> SelectScreening[Select a screening<br/>movie / date / time / screen]

    SelectScreening --> LoadSeats[Load this screening's<br/>seat map]
    LoadSeats --> LookupCustomer{Registered customer?}
    LookupCustomer -- Yes --> SearchCustomer[Search customer<br/>load tier + points]
    LookupCustomer -- No --> SelectGuest[Select Guest<br/>no discount, no points]
    SearchCustomer --> SelectSeats
    SelectGuest --> SelectSeats

    SelectSeats[Select one or more seats<br/>on the seat map]
    SelectSeats --> SeatFree{Seat already booked?}
    SeatFree -- Yes --> SeatTakenMsg[Show 'seat already taken'<br/>remove from selection]
    SeatTakenMsg --> SelectSeats
    SeatFree -- No --> ShowBreakdown

    ShowBreakdown["Show price breakdown<br/>subtotal / tier discount / GST 15% / total"]
    ShowBreakdown --> ChoosePayment[Choose payment method<br/>Cash / Card / Voucher]

    ChoosePayment --> IsCash{Cash selected?}
    IsCash -- Yes --> EnterCash[Enter cash amount received]
    EnterCash --> EnoughCash{Cash >= total?}
    EnoughCash -- No --> CashError[Show error:<br/>not enough cash]
    CashError --> EnterCash
    EnoughCash -- Yes --> CalcChange[Calculate change due]
    IsCash -- No --> ConfirmClick

    CalcChange --> ConfirmClick[Staff clicks Confirm Booking]

    ConfirmClick --> ReserveSeats[Reserve every selected seat]
    ReserveSeats --> DoubleBooked{Seat taken<br/>between selection and confirm?}
    DoubleBooked -- Yes --> ConflictError[Show error, cancel this booking<br/>seat stays taken by the other booking]
    ConflictError --> End1([End - booking not created])

    DoubleBooked -- No --> CalcTotal[Calculate final price<br/>Booking.calculateTotal]
    CalcTotal --> AwardPoints[Award loyalty points<br/>Customer.updatePoints]
    AwardPoints --> CheckTier{Points cross a<br/>tier threshold?}
    CheckTier -- Yes --> UpgradeTier[Auto-upgrade tier<br/>log to Membership History]
    CheckTier -- No --> SavePayment
    UpgradeTier --> SavePayment

    SavePayment[Process payment<br/>Payment.processPayment]
    SavePayment --> SaveBooking[Save Booking + Payment<br/>to the database]
    SaveBooking --> GenerateReceipt[Generate receipt<br/>itemised breakdown, points, staff name]
    GenerateReceipt --> ShowReceipt[Display receipt to staff]
    ShowReceipt --> SeatShown[Seat map updates:<br/>booked seat now shows as taken]
    SeatShown --> End2([End - booking complete])